{"tid":1701133,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"英國 Twitter 數據分析","createTime":"2019-11-09T01:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T01:43:22.000Z","uid":338032,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6f70cfc4965dc137a2d9afb95210be75ac283625","tid":1701133,"uid":338032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:22:15.000Z","msg":"最近有班<span style=\"color: red;\">巴</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">絲</span>打好想知道國際戰上既 Twitter 究竟有咩話題，同埋有d咩人關注。加上宜家英國就黎大選，相信大家都好關注各界政客對香港政局睇法，所以做左以下既好簡單的分析。<br />\n<br />\n我地<span style=\"color: red;\">巴</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">絲</span>打分析左最近 (*) 由英國 post 出黎同香港有關既 Tweets。首先，我地拎左一個星期左右既數據，第一步就係用 graph theory 去分析咩人會 tweet/retweet 同香港相關既貼文。我地發現英國政界人物其實對香港時局都非常關注。<br />\n<br />\n(*) 由於 Twitter official API 所限，只可以拎到大概 7-9 日既數據。我地只係用左由 25/10 到 3/11 期間既 data。<br />\n<br />\n以下圖為例，@LindenBro &rarr; @LindenSis 單向箭嘴即表示 @LindenBro 發左 Tweet 並且在其中 mention 左另一個人 @LindenSis。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bHAt0M6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbHAt0M6.jpg&h=3e325be6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地用呢個方法highlight左好幾位英國政界人士 (並且用顏色 tag 左)，以下係佢地主要觀點 (大家快 d click 入去多謝人地出聲，又或者 retweet 幫拖)：<br />\n<br />\n- <strong>蘇格蘭民族黨 (SNP) 國會議員 @StewartMcDonald</strong> (<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Q1PfPA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Q1PfPA&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=e99dff7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Q1PfPA</a>)<br />\n反對 DQ 黃之峰，經常同居英港人會面，關注居英權問題，支持反極權示威<br />\n<br />\n- <strong>保守黨 人權委員會  @benedictrogers</strong> (<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2K3jwJH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2K3jwJH&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=a367839a\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2K3jwJH</a>) 及 <strong>@lukedepulford</strong> (<a href=\"https://bit.ly/32uKJvh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32uKJvh&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=d4a6e107\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/32uKJvh</a>)<br />\n要求英國大學嚴懲何君堯，支持制裁極權政府，正在參與制定英國版香港人權法<br />\n<br />\n- <strong>保守黨 國會議員助理 @EKTBanks</strong> (<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2NteRTF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NteRTF&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=64cf7ac3\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2NteRTF</a>)<br />\n關注學術自由、中共紅色審查，帶頭聯署反對 University of York 清拆連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n- <strong>工黨 Broxtowe 選區主席 @Pete_Radcliff </strong> (<a href=\"https://bit.ly/36FO5Po\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36FO5Po&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=0b69ebf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/36FO5Po</a>)<br />\n嚴厲批評投共左膠政棍 George Galloway (多次上CCTV發表撐中共言論)，關注MTR與港共關系，呼籲國際工人運動關注香港示威，經常發 Tweet 積極支持港人勇武抗爭<br />\n<br />\n- <strong>上議院終身貴族議員  綠黨 (Green Party) 前任黨魁 @natalieben</strong> (<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2K45aZU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2K45aZU&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=b12093a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2K45aZU</a>)<br />\n關注警暴，承認英國對香港有歷史責任，要求執政黨譴責港共政權  綠黨聲明 (<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2p5kwWE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2p5kwWE&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=658d2abd\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2p5kwWE</a>)  <br />\n<br />\n除此以外，我地亦用左好簡單既 text mining 方法分析左英國 Twitter 最近有咩主要話題，以下係 9 大話題及其關鍵詞：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMyrNxu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMyrNxu.png&h=68b5761f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家可以清楚見到 &lsquo;Lord Alton&rsquo; 係非常 trending 既主要關鍵詞 (佢係之前號召褫奪何君堯博士學位既上議院議員) ，除此之外仲可以見到其它 topic，例如連結 Catalonia、黃之峰被禁參選 (&lsquo;Joshua&rsquo;, &lsquo;Wong&rsquo;, &lsquo;disqualification&rsquo;)、以及同警暴相關既字詞 (&lsquo;blood&rsquo;, &lsquo;violent&rsquo;...)<br />\n<br />\n西方政界既光譜非常廣闊，大家見得到左中右政黨都對香港時局有相當既關注。加入 Twitter 國際戰線既手足可以用唔同角度去推廣香港議題！<br />\n<br />\n仲有，我地用既 code 係可以比大家睇到的，歡迎大家攞黎自用 ：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JWuJvT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JWuJvT&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=3027b801\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JWuJvT</a><br />\n<br />\n最後加多句，英國 12/12 就係大選，各位居於英國既手足記得要投票，合力踢走英國既親中撐共勢力。大家亦可以寫信或約見所屬選區既國會議員，討論包括香港時局在內既一切事務。有<span style=\"color: red;\">巴</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">絲</span>開左個<strong>英國大選Telegram 群組</strong>，大家可以加入：<a href=\"http://t.me/UKVoterAction4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUKVoterAction4HK&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=91e84979\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/UKVoterAction4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">#光復香港 #時代革命<br />\n#StandWithHongKong #RevolutionOfOurTime<br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"6f63c881abfa1d220395ea09d226d932bd79d75e","tid":1701133,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:22:48.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去rt + like + reply</span><br />\nSenator Rubio都知道周同學死訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=b060ffcf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&h=c4dc6427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n（最新）Senator Scott 都出聲講議員被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006%3Fs%3D19&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOJE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=d03e7a59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006%3Fs%3D19&h=01c0cece\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n（突發）Senator Hawley 同 Solomon Yue 知道議員被拉！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1700966</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"19d308f76c8e6e4f16ba79a1705868cb3c7b04fe","tid":1701133,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:25:20.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"b15930dd08798f891db427f6d09737e97492911b","tid":1701133,"uid":26190,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:44:22.000Z","msg":"小妹想講 你地好有心做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但有個少少睇法<br />\n<br />\n睇Twitter真係唔會估到佢地議員取態係點 建議你地加返個Lib Dem 雖然佢地大部份議員無提過香港 但佢地會阻到脫歐 始終係第三大黨<br />\n<br />\n英國MP講大話多人人皆知 佢地玩字眼係比香港人高好多班<br />\n<br />\n不過你地有心就全力做"},{"pid":"3e3bbd0a2d4ef1c5cad0a136b100930517aa274d","tid":1701133,"uid":129202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:48:47.000Z","msg":"Pish 如果有埋python package 就更好"},{"pid":"1c02e8bef9c94ebad20bd42c0f3318db1e613467","tid":1701133,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:50:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f5de77d9956c7d4995b3bd694cef3961e80d2d0","tid":1701133,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccffd603f3db163045684473951a36863359a85a","tid":1701133,"uid":64946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:01:12.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"6d8ea760eb1b2380ff40eff5c159b9a5c707bad0","tid":1701133,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:14:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29e88d6de25211957523dcd725e4d18859d7b97d","tid":1701133,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:15:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5e76a5a155b7a9a2163a86341934063d528a678","tid":1701133,"uid":338032,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b15930dd08798f891db427f6d09737e97492911b","tid":1701133,"uid":26190,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:44:22.000Z","msg":"小妹想講 你地好有心做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但有個少少睇法<br />\n<br />\n睇Twitter真係唔會估到佢地議員取態係點 建議你地加返個Lib Dem 雖然佢地大部份議員無提過香港 但佢地會阻到脫歐 始終係第三大黨<br />\n<br />\n英國MP講大話多人人皆知 佢地玩字眼係比香港人高好多班<br />\n<br />\n不過你地有心就全力做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:15:12.000Z","msg":"其實絲打講得冇錯，唔係個個MP 都有 twitter account的。例如為咗香港做咗好多嘢既 Fiona Bruce MP，佢連twitter 都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋研究緊可唔可以用國會發言紀錄 (Hansard) 來分析議員對香港同中國嘅睇法，係親定係反，定係廢噏、揼波鍾，又或者有咩主要關注議題之類。而家仲諗緊下一步點做好，有橋大家分享下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c89eccb6e6e29caec6b36c2ff1bfc19e21a1181","tid":1701133,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:15:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26f06e5ad017fb87c9325e55e7752fd20b3c0e75","tid":1701133,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:15:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"703f28fe766ca985b197c574661be1a3e203b972","tid":1701133,"uid":242647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T02:15:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6eda6d78055690a38c8cbae5343c3eb138a5b6fc","tid":1701133,"uid":338032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e3bbd0a2d4ef1c5cad0a136b100930517aa274d","tid":1701133,"uid":129202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:48:47.000Z","msg":"Pish 如果有埋python package 就更好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-